title: The Venk
author: littlevenk
pages:
#- There lived two humble beings in what was their humble abode... until the great attack. 

It was DOL5N and amush who attacked on that day in January of 2013, I was pearled. Clone was pearled. tbeau1 was pearled. So many lives gone, so much blood shed.
#- Fast forward a few days later into the next week. Clone tells Venk that amush has been pearled.

A day later or so, the infamous Y_ankees was banned from all enterance to the server.

